I used to live next door to Rocky Mountain National Pass, and went riding in
the Rockies last fall. I miss the altitude, the views, and the summer snow :-)
So I was delighted as we crossed into the tundra biome and then got our first
glimpses of snow:

{% flickr-img :photo-id 35554352474
              :album-id 72157684801453550
              :user forgottenroadsmx
              :width 240 %}
{% flickr-img :photo-id 35554355314
